Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:19.45,EpTitle,Title,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,1)\fscx181\fscy181\pos(736,263.334)}First Night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:19.45,EpTitle,Title,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,1)\fscx330\fscy330\pos(726.333,536.667)}"Recipe"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:32.24,Default - Flashback,Husband,0,0,0,,You don't want to forget about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:35.43,Default - Flashback,Husband,0,0,0,,so always set the timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:39.99,Default - Flashback,Husband,0,0,0,,Pomodoro sauce should have \Na nice, full flavor,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:42.40,Default - Flashback,Husband,0,0,0,,so I make it using butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.66,0:00:51.00,Default - Flashback,Husband,0,0,0,,Once it's spread out evenly, add the stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.56,0:00:54.86,Default - Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,You put in a lot, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.17,0:00:56.36,Default - Flashback,Husband,0,0,0,,Yes, put in a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:00.72,Default - Flashback,Husband,0,0,0,,Boil down the tomato sauce first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.53,0:01:02.98,Default - Flashback,Husband,0,0,0,,That way...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:05.46,Default - Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,Its savory flavor is further condensed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:44.49,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:46.51,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,Here's dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:51.54,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:01.89,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:05.24,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,does it taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:11.58,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,There's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:16.99,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.81,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,You had to make pomodoro
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,for the first time once \Nyourself, right, Azuma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:47.69,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,Oh? That's a funny thing to ask \Nout of the blue, Nagi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:50.27,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,look up a recipe or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:58.48,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,Well... I was taught.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.50,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,Very patiently taught.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:03.28,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,Starting with how to boil the spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:06.75,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,To start by setting the timer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:11.05,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,That's just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:17.26,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,So do you add any of your \Nown personal touches to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:23.62,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,I do, but it's nearly the same \Npomodoro as yours is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:26.69,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,The
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,flavor of your pomodoro has always
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,been my aspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:36.50,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,So you've said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.93,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,Ever since you first made it at my house...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:45.65,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,Since I was able to start this job...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:48.95,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,And in the three years \Nsince you took me in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:57.02,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,In the beginning, your pomodoro \Nwas the flavor I strived for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:01.34,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,But the more I tried,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:04.61,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,the more I realized I could \Nnever reach your level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:12.20,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,"How did Azuma-san get her pomodoro \Nto taste the way it does?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:14.79,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,When I thought about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:17.83,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,I finally realized that it wasn't \Nyou I should be watching,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:23.64,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,but what you, yourself, were looking at.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:30.92,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,After my two years in Milan, \Nstarting two days from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:33.38,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,I'll come back as a chef
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:37.67,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,with the ability to look much farther \Ninto the distance, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:43.53,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,So until then, Azuma-san, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.70,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,Please keep watching over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:50.80,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,these past three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:00.07,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,Thank you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.13,Default - Italics,Azuma,0,0,0,,Silly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:06.33,Default - Italics,Azuma,0,0,0,,There's no secret to my pomodoro's flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:11.90,Default - Italics,Azuma,0,0,0,,I guess this is how it feels \Nto be given too much credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:18.37,Default - Italics,Azuma,0,0,0,,I was like you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:36.12,Default - Italics,Azuma,0,0,0,,I only now understand
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:40.00,Default - Italics,Azuma,0,0,0,,how selfish it is to make \Nsomeone your role model,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:44.53,Default - Italics,Azuma,0,0,0,,and how cowardly I was to not \Ntry to stand at your level.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:49.22,Default - Flashback,Husband,0,0,0,,Once it's spread out evenly, add the stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:51.37,Default - Flashback,Azuma,0,0,0,,You put in a lot, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:52.93,Default - Flashback,Husband,0,0,0,,Yes, put in a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:56.96,Default - Italics,Azuma,0,0,0,,The strange guilt you feel when \Nsomeone looks up to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.35,Default - Italics,Azuma,0,0,0,,The awkwardness,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.06,Default - Italics,Azuma,0,0,0,,the responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:05.25,Default - Italics,Azuma,0,0,0,,and the separation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:20.48,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,So now I'm sending off a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:24.22,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:28.30,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,Just talking about the former \Nowner of that suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:32.20,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,What? It's not yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.99,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. \NGo on, now. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:44.62,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,Azuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:48.93,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,When I come back to Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:51.84,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,let's have a contest to find \Nout which tastes better,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:55.25,Default,Nagi,0,0,0,,my pomodoro or yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.78,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,I'll squash you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:22.96,Default,Husband,0,0,0,,I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.44,Default,Husband,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:27.80,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:34.42,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,I just hope he doesn't come back before \Nhe's finished, like someone else I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:37.38,Default,Azuma,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:44.81,Default,Husband,0,0,0,,You know, I wish you wouldn't \Njust give away my old suitcase.
